'''2013年穆尔龙卷风'''（{{lang-en|'''2013 Moore Tornado'''}}）发生在2013年5月20日，主要襲擊美国[[俄克拉何马州|俄克拉何马州]][[奧克拉荷馬市|奧克拉荷馬市]]南方郊區的[[穆尔_(俄克拉何马州)|穆尔市]]，强度[[改良藤田级数|EF5]]级，造成至少24人死亡，<ref name="Retuers521">{{cite web|author=Carey Gillam and Ian Simpson|publisher=Reuters|date=2013-05-21|accessdate=2013-05-21|title=Oklahoma lowers tornado death toll amid frantic search|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/21/us-usa-tornadoes-idUSBRE94J0TK20130521|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924181434/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/05/21/us-usa-tornadoes-idUSBRE94J0TK20130521|dead-url=no}}</ref>240人受伤<ref name="injured-145">{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/05/20/us/oklahoma-tornado-developments/index.html |title=Oklahoma City tornado: Get the latest developments in this disaster |publisher=CNN |date=2013-05-20 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gm5c0Ssh?url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/05/20/us/oklahoma-tornado-developments/index.html |archivedate=2013-05-21 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-05-22 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://kfor.com/2013/05/20/tornado-wipes-out-homes-schools-businesses-in-moore/|title=VIDEO: Tornado wipes out homes, schools, businesses in Moore|publisher=KFOR|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2013-05-20|archive-date=2020-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201145303/https://kfor.com/2013/05/20/tornado-wipes-out-homes-schools-businesses-in-moore/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2013/05/20135205174918331.html|title=Deadly tornado strikes near Oklahoma City|publisher=Al Jazeera English|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2013-05-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gm5qXZCR?url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2013/05/20135205174918331.html|archivedate=2013-05-21|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/05/20/oklahoma-city-tornado-2013_n_3308384.html|title=Oklahoma City Tornado 2013: Twister Makes Landfall Near Capital|publisher=The Huffington Post|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2013-05-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gm6261jj?url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/05/20/oklahoma-city-tornado-2013_n_3308384.html|archivedate=2013-05-21|deadurl=no}}</ref>。该龙卷风在美国中部夏令时间2:56pm出现（19:56 [[协调世界时|UTC]]），在地上肆虐40分钟，影响面积达{{convert|20|mi|km|adj=on}}宽。<ref>{{cite web|title=Massive tornado rips through Oklahoma City suburbs|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-22604251|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2013-05-20|date=2013-05-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gm6EO9Gr?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-22604251|archivedate=2013-05-21|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=McClam|first=Erin|title='Major damage' as huge tornado rips through neighborhoods south of Oklahoma City|url=http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/05/20/18375741-major-damage-as-huge-tornado-rips-through-neighborhoods-south-of-oklahoma-city?lite|publisher=NBC News|accessdate=2013-05-20|date=2013-05-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gm7Qwnfg?url=http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/05/20/18375741-at-least-51-killed-including-20-children-as-tornado-tears-through-oklahoma-leaving-miles-of-debris?lite|archivedate=2013-05-21|deadurl=no}}</ref>龙卷风在俄克拉何马州[[穆尔_(俄克拉荷马州)|穆尔]]市经过，强度最大时超过{{convert|2|mi|km}}宽。<ref name="Valencia">{{cite news|author=Nick Valencia|author2=Catherine Shoichet|author3=Dana Ford|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2013-05-20|publisher=CNN U.S.|title=Two-mile-wide tornado slams Oklahoma City area, killing at least 10|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/05/20/us/severe-weather/index.html|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gm7diFIy?url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/05/20/us/severe-weather/index.html|archivedate=2013-05-21|deadurl=no}}</ref>

==灾情==
龙卷风经过地区受到毁灭性打击。<ref name="usatoday1">{{cite news|title=Tornado had winds over 200 mph|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/weather/2013/05/21/oklahoma-tornadoes/2344923/|last1=Hughes|first1=Trevor|last2=Jervis|first2=Rick|last3=Shorman|first3=Jonthan|last4=Welch|first4=William M.|newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2013-05-21|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918154716/https://www.usatoday.com/story/weather/2013/05/21/oklahoma-tornadoes/2344923/|dead-url=no}}</ref>受灾最严重的是两所学校[[Moore_Public_Schools#Elementary_schools|Briarwood小学]]和[[Moore_Public_Schools#Elementary_schools|Plaza Towers小学]]。在Plaza Towers小学，龙卷风来袭时有75名学生、老师在场。<ref name="TheProvince">{{cite news|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2013-05-20|publisher=The Province|title=Oklahoma City tornado: Reports of 75 children in devastated grade school|url=http://www.theprovince.com/news/Reports+children+grade+school+devastated+Oklahoma+City+tornado/8410350/story.html|last=Talley|first=Tim|agency=Associated Press|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130612043011/http://www.theprovince.com/news/Reports+children+grade+school+devastated+Oklahoma+City+tornado/8410350/story.html|archivedate=2013-06-12}}</ref>最终有9人确认遇难。<ref name="Retuers521"/><ref name="NYTMay21">{{cite news|title=Vast Oklahoma Tornado Kills at Least 91|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/21/us/tornado-oklahoma.html|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2013-05-21|date=2013-05-20|last1=Oxford|first1=Nick|last2=Schwirtz|first2=Michael|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125032824/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/21/us/tornado-oklahoma.html|archivedate=2020-11-25|deadurl=no}}</ref> 穆尔市的医疗中心也严重损毁，所幸没有人员伤亡。所有病人被转移其他医院<ref name="usatoday1"/>。

==善后==
[[File:U.S._President_Barack_Obama_talks_on_the_telephone_with_Oklahoma_Governor_Mary_Fallin_following_the_2013_Moore_tornado.jpg|thumb]]从[[椭圆形办公室|椭圆形办公室]]给[[俄克拉何马州|俄克拉何马州]]打电话]]
[[联邦紧急事务管理署|联邦紧急事务管理署]]（FEMA）积极部署搜索与救援团队到龙卷风受灾地区，并且派人员前往指挥。<ref name="FEMA">[https://www.fema.gov/news-release/2013/05/20/fema-federal-partners-support-response-severe-storms-oklahoma FEMA, Federal Partners Support Response to Severe Storms in Oklahoma] {{Wayback|url=https://www.fema.gov/news-release/2013/05/20/fema-federal-partners-support-response-severe-storms-oklahoma |date=20200201145150 }}, [[聯邦緊急事務管理署|Federal Emergency Management Agency]], May 20, 2013.</ref>俄克拉何马州也派出[[国民警卫队|国民警卫队]]搜救。美国总统[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]从办公室打电话到奧克拉荷馬市。<ref>{{cite web|title=Oklahoma governor calls out National Guard|url=http://www.khou.com/news/national/Oklahoma-governor-calls-out-National-Guard-208229051.html|publisher=KHOU TV|accessdate=2013-05-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130620153648/http://www.khou.com/news/national/Oklahoma-governor-calls-out-National-Guard-208229051.html|archivedate=2013-06-20}}</ref>白宫表示，奥巴马总统告诉俄克拉何马州[[州长|州长]]，总统夫妇很关心俄克拉何马州人民，联邦政府会继续关注灾情进展，他说州长若需要联邦提供帮助时可与他保持进一步密切联系<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2013/05/20/readout-president-s-call-oklahoma-governor-mary-fallin |title=Readout of the President’s Call with Oklahoma Governor Mary Fallin | The White House |publisher=Whitehouse.gov |date=2013-04-01 |accessdate=2013-05-21 |archive-date=2016-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229211457/https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2013/05/20/readout-president-s-call-oklahoma-governor-mary-fallin |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

龙卷风导致38,000户居民断电<ref name="Valencia"/>。奥巴马宣布俄克拉何马州受到重大灾害，宣布提高联邦援助给受灾地区。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boston.com/news/weather/2013/05/20/obama-declares-major-disaster-oklahoma/HhzzzIWG55dgOrW8tsoKBP/story.html |title=Obama declares major disaster in Oklahoma - News |publisher=Boston.com |date=2013-05-17 |accessdate=2013-05-21}}</ref>

